Habe: 43 (G. millegranosa cited as type species, but no diagnosis); nor from Beu & Ponder (1979) Records of the Australian Museum 32(1): 9 (G. millegranosa cited as type species by original designation, but no diagnosis and Galeoastraea listed in synonymy of Bolma)
